title: Episode 16 | “I Saw Your Speech…” (feat. HitBoy)
description: The guys sit down in LA with HitBoy, coming off the release of his collaborative effort ‘What You Expect’ with Big Sean. Hit-Boy opens up about his process working with different artists (2:34), his accidental viral rant shading Kanye’s rollout (5:49), an honest opinion on Quentin Miller (11:47), Big Sean’s growth (30:18), + more!
author: newrorymal@gmail.com (More Sauce)
